      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To repeal Public Law 114-145 to ensure that the Drug Enforcement Administration has the authority to carry out needed enforcement actions for drug diversion control investigations and operations to combat the opioid epidemic.</title>
